{"tid":359471,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"LIHKG 整咗做progressive web app","createTime":"2017-08-14T13:55:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-15T12:42:52.000Z","uid":67527,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"21e5d4b1f86e2ac5c19ea1e6d5ad43fc7aebfa88","tid":359471,"uid":67527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T13:55:10.000Z","msg":"Android chrome已經有彈出嚟(chrome點解會彈個install出嚟可以自己搵Google講progressive web app個blog)<br />\n<br />\n頭先502/503咗一輪，唔知係咪就係update依樣嘢，同埋LIHKG Android個所謂native app好似唔work，係咁遇到錯誤1000"},{"pid":"7aecfe095cc8272d126162679545e500521c52eb","tid":359471,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T14:14:31.000Z","msg":"native太撚廢"},{"pid":"b00729c7e623bbb8785aed7752faed8552a60bd8","tid":359471,"uid":122859,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T14:36:00.000Z","msg":"居然有人留意到到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實 PWA 左都一排。不過 Add 左 home screen 會出 404 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下個 release 會 fix 返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edb23dcff986e5e8ca735facd6d540557f8eb8bb","tid":359471,"uid":2950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T14:41:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>居然有人留意到到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實 PWA 左都一排。不過 Add 左 home screen 會出 404 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下個 release 會 fix 返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新account<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d93beb524443f1e0aad22fb9aaf1f32487c2c43","tid":359471,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T22:47:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/15/064710_8125a16010f41bf84da14642a89