/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下個 release 會 fix 返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nReact pwa?"},{"pid":"f0e226d26b7cb81dce1f148f17e1dea51bbf2515","tid":359471,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T00:35:32.000Z","msg":"究竟呢個所謂PWA, 係咪真野黎, e.g. offline都用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b687448700dd183cbbcda0005ebe96bf671910ea","tid":359471,"uid":133387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T00:38:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>究竟呢個所謂PWA, 係咪真野黎, e.g. offline都用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nPWA 真係好咩? Apple 都唔睇好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fb0941d2403be57799f33e6a1f700c01890f16b","tid":359471,"uid":23011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T01:16:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>究竟呢個所謂PWA, 係咪真野黎, e.g. offline都用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nPWA 真係好咩? Apple 都唔睇好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nApple緊係唔睇好啦 , 呢家咁多應用為app而app , 如果大推pwa仲有無咁多人係App Store放程式? 仲點賺上架費同對住個應用數量打飛機? 另外呢家Apple咁崇中 , Google個Notification又淨得GCM入唔到大陸境內 , Apple支持完都唔會有好處<br />\n<br />\n講返lihkg,我又好好奇論壇每次更新內容量都咁多咁大,pwa到底有幾大優勢? 講真就算俾你做到offine , 淨係睇得堆舊post都無乜用 , 亦好難有咁大個cache俾你裝咁多post"},{"pid":"26bd5e1e7f707b0634a28b069db8e3ab8b68863d","tid":359471,"uid":67527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T01:16:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>究竟呢個所謂PWA, 係咪真野黎, e.g. offline都用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係要睇下個App點set啲caching，如果連js css html嗰啲都無set cache，就其實offline係完全用唔到嘅"},{"pid":"b87260e410ad87bcc745c389898a4e102767739f","tid":359471,"uid":67527,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T01:33:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>究竟呢個所謂PWA, 係咪真野黎, e.g. offline都用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nPWA 真係好咩? Apple 都唔睇好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nApple緊係唔睇好啦 , 呢家咁多應用為app而app , 如果大推pwa仲有無咁多人係App Store放程式? 仲點賺上架費同對住個應用數量打飛機? 另外呢家Apple咁崇中 , Google個Notification又淨得GCM入唔到大陸境內 , Apple支持完都唔會有好處<br />\n<br />\n講返lihkg,我又好好奇論壇每次更新內容量都咁多咁大,pwa到底有幾大優勢? 講真就算俾你做到offine , 淨係睇得堆舊post都無乜用 , 亦好難有咁大個cache俾你裝咁多post</blockquote><br />\n其實所謂Native lihkg app咪都係咁。但係其實用pwa有個好處係native畀唔到，就係永遠都update，因為啲cache係用service worker控制，service worker唔到用戶控制，基本上用戶連update咗都唔知(除非改UI加功能)，係宜家好多用家成日鬧做咩成日update嘅情況，其實pwa係幾好。"},{"pid":"78c59ff775a35eea027562ed235dbf090aaef10a","tid":359471,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T03:52:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>究竟呢個所謂PWA, 係咪真野黎, e.g. offline都用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係要睇下個App點set啲caching，如果連js css html嗰啲都無set cache，就其實offline係完全用唔到嘅</blockquote><br />\n唔知呀, 剩係知道如果要offline用, 就要加Service Workers呢個HTML5 API先得囉. 唔知LIHKG有冇加到呢? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81f7afdbe81b82b44e32026a5e9c792e74b0ff28","tid":359471,"uid":67527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T04:08:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>究竟呢個所謂PWA, 係咪真野黎, e.g. offline都用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係要睇下個App點set啲caching，如果連js css html嗰啲都無set cache，就其實offline係完全用唔到嘅</blockquote><br />\n唔知呀, 剩係知道如果要offline用, 就要加Service Workers呢個HTML5 API先得囉. 唔知LIHKG有冇加到呢? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nProgressive web app一定有(至少做到chrome肯彈出嚟問用戶就一定有)<br />\n頭先睇咗Lihkg個service worker，都見到至少有cache js同css"},{"pid":"5727d4a54fb6d6042329348bf1c6e3b57c26f526","tid":359471,"uid":6556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:50:28.000Z","msg":"冇彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd563bf913b9da9fba2e49d467e6183268da99cd","tid":359471,"uid":6556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:57:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己 Add to Home screen 就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f056e47112c654d21b48f8b5f37474a085aff09","tid":359471,"uid":4258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:05:06.000Z","msg":"好用過app<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"420fe67d831196e1e3e125bd7a8333d80768e4f4","tid":359471,"uid":6556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:42:52.000Z","msg":"根本 Android version 冇咗啲嘢又一直都冇加<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}